## Review Checklist

Before marking a task complete:

### Code Quality
- [ ] TypeScript compiles without errors
- [ ] ESLint passes without warnings
- [ ] Unit tests pass
- [ ] Coverage meets target
- [ ] No `any` types introduced
- [ ] No `@ts-ignore` added
- [ ] No `console.log` in source

### Architecture
- [ ] Game logic in `packages/core`
- [ ] No Discord imports in `packages/core`
- [ ] API calls Prisma through services
- [ ] Transactions for multi-step mutations
- [ ] Audit logs created for player and admin actions

### Testing
- [ ] Core rules have unit tests
- [ ] Edge cases covered (zero, max, boundary)
- [ ] Error cases tested
- [ ] Integration tests for services (if applicable)

### Documentation
- [ ] New files documented in docstrings
- [ ] `kb/` updated if system behavior changed
- [ ] `docs/` updated if game rules changed
- [ ] `README.md` updated if build process changed

