## Test-Driven Development (Optional but Recommended)

For complex game mechanics, follow TDD:

```
1. Write the test first (it will fail)
2. Implement the minimum code to pass
3. Refactor
4. Repeat
```

This is especially valuable for:
- New cultivation modes
- Breakthrough tribulation mechanics
- Alchemy quality calculations
- Combat damage formulas
- Economy balancing formulas
